===Logic 8:Recording tempo changes in realtime===
----


To create real time tempo events in Logic


Go to the record settings ( '''Settings/Recording''' ) 


[[Image:Logic Settings record menu.png]]



In the dialog box that appears click '''Allow Tempo Change Recording'''



[[Image:Logic allow tempo change recording check box.png]]





Now if you record in real time and move the tempo display in the transport, these changes will get recorded to the tempo track.





[[Image:Logic tempo display .png]]



